  "title": "ISic001397. Epitaph for Glykera",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-11</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\"><span data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Γλυκέρα\">Γλυκέρ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>α</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"χρηστ\n                    ὰ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρηστ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ὰ</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησες</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span> · <span data-text=\"νγ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"νγ\">νγ</span>´ ❦ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Γλυκέρα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Γλυκέρα\">Γλυκέρα</span>  <span data-text=\"χρηστὰ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρηστὰ</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησες</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"νγ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"νγ\">νγ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-11</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\"><span data-text=\"Γλυκέρ\n                    α\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Γλυκέρα\">ΓΛΥΚΕΡ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Α</span></span></span><span data-text=\"χρηστ\n                    ὰ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣΤ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>Α</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΣ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>·<span data-text=\"νγ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"νγ\">ΝΓ</span>❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Γλυκέρα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Γλυκέρα\">ΓΛΥΚΕΡΑ</span><span data-text=\"χρηστὰ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣΤΑ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"νγ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"νγ\">ΝΓ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001397_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-11\" src=\"ISic001397_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001397.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-11\" src=\"ISic001397-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001397_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-11\" src=\"ISic001397_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001397_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-11\" src=\"ISic001397_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>text from autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Glykera, worthy one, farewell! you lived 53 years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> anonymous 1844 992 no.3 </li><li> Ansaldi 1851 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/724748\" target=\"_blank\">51 no. 14</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002182\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002182</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">578</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Neatly carved, regular letters of slightly uneven height (not v-cut, simple groove). Lunate epsilon and sigma, alpha with extended upper stroke, slight serifs to most strokes. Single interpunct before age.</p> Line 1  26-28 (Ε is 20)  Line 2  21-23 (Σ is 18)  Line 3  23-25 (Ε is 20)  Line 4  20-24  Line 5  21-22  Interlineation line 1 to 2  10  Interlineation line 2 to 3  10  Interlineation line 3 to 4  15  Interlineation line 4 to 5  10  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
